<h1 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
    🔐 Your Security Code
</h1>

<p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">
    We received a request to verify your identity. Use the code below to complete your action securely.
</p>

<div style="background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2); padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; color: white; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9;">Your Verification Code</h2>
    <div style="font-size: 48px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
        {{otp}}
    </div>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">
        Valid for {{expiryMinutes}} minutes
    </p>
</div>

<div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 30px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #856404; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🛡️ Security Tips:</h4>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #856404;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Never share this code with anyone</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Arena will never ask for your code via phone or email</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">This code expires in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes</li>
        <li>If you didn't request this, please contact support immediately</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Need Help?</a>
</div>

<p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    Having trouble? Copy and paste this code manually: <strong>{{otp}}</strong>
</p>

<div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
        This is an automated security message. Please do not reply to this email.
    </p>
</div>